# USGA Topology Map Links

These links are for the latest topo maps from the USGS
Not all of the US is in this list
The files are very large pdfs, up to 60+Mb per file
They are sorted by state

To generate this list
- source website https://viewer.nationalmap.gov/basic
- Select the checkbox for US Topo
- Select the checkbox for US Topo Current under the Map section
- use the selection tool on the map on the website, box, point, address, etc...
- you can zoom in and manipulate the map to get to the location you want
- select the "Show Availability" link on the left hand side near the "US Topo"
  checkbox you selected earlier.  This will display all topo maps available
- I use the box selector and select the counties or state I want
- once done, click the "Find Products" button in the left window
- this will generate a list of products
- you can export the list (URLS) to csv or txt file now by selecting the "Save
  as Text" or "Save as CSV" link
- this file is not unix compatible, so if you use wget, please use dos2unix or
  some other utility to convert it
